## Scope

This brain is **self-contained to this repo**. It depends on nothing outside it —
no external service, no shared vault, no cross-repo registry. Every fact it holds
originates from this repo's docs, code, decisions, and working sessions.

The brain is the orchestrator's long-term memory. It is NOT a task list (tasks live in
`{{HOME}}/INDEX.md`), NOT a changelog (that's git), and NOT a copy of the code
(entity pages MAP into code via `maps_to:`, they never paste it).

